{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8e9429aea7","title":"毛泽东给江青的几封信和批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c66039edc7","index":0,"year":1974,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"8e9429aea7"}],"tags":[{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c27c59e4bc","type":"title","text":"给江青的几封信和批语","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"8e1363add0","type":"appellation","text":"江青：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"13dfe80e87","type":"paragraph","text":"不见还好些。过去多年同你谈的，你有好些不执行，多见何益？有马列书在，有我的书在，你就是不研究。我重病在身，八十一了，也不体谅。你有特权，我死了，看你怎么办？你也是个大事不讨论，小事天天送的人。请你考虑。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"02204719c0","type":"paragraph","text":" 3. 20","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"63bde968ab","type":"appellation","text":"江青：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"a4422dbfaa","type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平同志出国是我的意见，你不要反对为好。小心谨慎，不要反对我的提议。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"3049ec85d4","type":"paragraph","text":" 3. 27","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"70489fa44e","type":"appellation","text":"江青：","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"1f697ea667","type":"paragraph","text":"两信收。前后不一。党的大势不错，悲观不好。不要动摇。前途是光明的，道路是曲折的。要团结百分之九十五以上的人。不要主观片观（面）。千万注意。牢骚太盛防肠断，风物长宜（放）眼量。不要请假。钱可略增。无限风光在险峰。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"521b549aa1","type":"paragraph","text":" 4. 17","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"9d1d760562","type":"appellation","text":"江青：","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"6ae9a9cfbe","type":"paragraph","text":"可读李固给黄琼书。就思想文章而论，都是一篇好文章。你的职务就是研究国内外动态，这已经是大任务了。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"47b5a53f61","type":"paragraph","text":"此事我对你说了多次，不要说没有工作。此嘱。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"},{"id":"a77f243127","type":"paragraph","text":" 11. 20","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7"}],"page":{"id":"3b7a79a93e","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8e9429aea7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}